data.enText: the act of preventing sb/sth from entering a place or taking part in sth

data.chText: 他对自己没有入选英格兰队感到失望。
data.enText: He was disappointed with his exclusion from the England squad.

data.chText: 瓶子里的空气排除后就产生真空。
data.enText: Exclusion of air creates a vacuum in the bottle.

data.chText: 她满脑子全是对过去的回忆，其他事情都不想了。
data.enText: Memories of the past filled her mind to the exclusion of all else.

data.chText: 不包括在内的人（或事物）；被排除在外的人（或事物）
data.enText: a person or thing that is not included in sth

data.chText: 检查一下保险单上不包括的项目。
data.enText: Check the list of exclusions in the insurance policy.
the act of deciding that sth is not possible
the exclusion of robbery as a motive
a situation in which a child is banned from attending school because of bad behaviour

data.chText: 把捣蛋的学生开除出学校
data.enText: the exclusion of disruptive students from school

data.chText: 一所学校在一周内就有两起开除学生的事是少有的。
data.enText: Two exclusions from one school in the same week is unusual.

simple_means.memory_skill: ex 出 + clus 关闭 + ion 表动作 → 排斥，排除在外

means: 不包括在内的人(或事物)
被排除在外的人(或事物)

tr: the act of forcing out someone or something
example: the ejection of troublemakers by the police
with the exception of the children, everyone was told the news

value.def: The exclusion of something is the act of deliberately not using, allowing, or considering it.

example.ex: It calls for the exclusion of all commercial lending institutions from the college loan program...
example.tran: 它提倡将所有商贷机构排除在高校贷款计划之外。
一些排除因素和限制条件比较适用。

value.def: Exclusion is the act of preventing someone from entering a place or taking part in an activity.

example.tran: 在政治权力上对女性的排斥

example.ex: A spokeswoman for Mr Prescott yesterday made it clear that he had been unhappy at his exclusion.
example.tran: 普雷斯科特先生的发言人昨天表明他对于自己被拒绝十分不满。

gramarinfo.label: usu with poss, oft N <l>from</l> n

value.def: If you do one thing to the exclusion of something else, you only do the first thing and do not do the second thing at all.

example.ex: Diane had dedicated her life to caring for him to the exclusion of all else.
example.tran: 黛安娜一生都在照顾他，对其他一切都无暇顾及。

gramarinfo.label: usu PHR after v, PHR n

trans: 排阻色谱法；筛析色谱法
排他（除外）原则；不相容原理
泡利不相容原理；不相容原理；泡利原理；保里不相容原理；保利不相容原理
